00:18:36.719 --> 00:18:52.400
analysis tasks, you can use this idea of dynamic documents. So the basic idea is that a data analysis report is basically a combination of your program code with some

00:18:52.400 --> 00:19:04.920
narratives to explain what your code is doing here. So here is a very simple example. For example, first we write some narratives like we built a linear regression

